<Content>Great location, Great owners, Modest / Decent Rooms I read the previous reviews before booking my 3 night stay at Hotel Gunia and I was quite pleased. The location is great and the owners are super nice...the minor drawback is the small size of the room. But hey, this is Europe, right? I would definitely stay here again and look forward to this nice comfortable hotel right in the middle of big / busy Berlin. 
