<Content>Great Place To Stay! Wonderful reasonable place to stay.Within a block or so of two main transportation station. Five minutes to KaDaVe and all. Yet on a quiet side street.Very spacious comfortable rooms. The hosts are some of the nicest, most accommodating people I have ever met in my world wide travel.If you are looking for 4 or 5 star luxury, go elsewhere. But if you want a safe, convenient, reasonable, comfortable, friendly spot, I don't think that you can do better. 
